      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on this noir detective novel set in a really gritty, decaying city. i need to flesh out the world a bit. can you give me a list of 5 'street-level' characters that would make the setting feel authentic? include their ethnicity and some personality traits for each so i can get a feel for them.",
